{"tid":558041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你九龍角落李軒朗班垃圾佔用學聯為咗選立法會？","createTime":"2018-02-12T02:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T04:56:52.000Z","uid":105451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3235d75a8d22df3704092770fc6787d6f8ebc1c3","tid":558041,"uid":105451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:15:27.000Z","msg":"hk01<br />\n<br />\n據了解，「九龍角落」於去年9月成立，在Facebook專頁上表明是九龍西地區組職。政界流傳，兼任組織執行委員會主席的現屆學聯秘書長李軒朗，有意競選由第二輪DQ產生的九龍西立法會議席空缺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/101508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F101508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=edb2a084&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f2bdfb378b0ed8aee221520473184b636fa37d9","tid":558041,"uid":105825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:27:58.000Z","msg":"一票不投九龍角落"},{"pid":"e32c7bea6cc5960272f32e43533c66bdd1cd3baf","tid":558041,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"退聯狗最後自己食埋學聯d資源嚟自己用"},{"pid":"e567bef4af79f69a3733d4313b5cae814b059549","tid":558041,"uid":105451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e32c7bea6cc5960272f32e43533c66bdd1cd3baf","tid":558041,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"退聯狗最後自己食埋學聯d資源嚟自己用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"九龍角落匪賊"}]}